highlights.text: “Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 248 weeks straight.
“Overpass Graffiti” by Ed Sheeran is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #14.
“Ghost Town” by Benson Boone is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 70 spots at #72.
Ed Sheeran has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Shivers” is the highest at #4.
